claim.claim-text:
An operation method of an electronic device, the method comprising:
determining if an object is detected at a first terminal and a second terminal among a plurality of terminals of an ear jack;
if an object is detected, calculating an impedance of the second terminal; and determining a type of the object according to the calculated impedance.
